actions.text: Read twice and referred to the Committee on Finance.
Committee on Finance. Ordered to be reported without amendment favorably.

official_title: A bill to suspend temporarily the duty on (6R-(6a,7B(Z)))-7-(((2-Amino-4-thiazolyl((carboxymethoxy) imino) acetyl) amino)-3-ethenyl-8-oxo-5-thia-1-azabicyclo(4.2.0.) oct-2-ene-2-carboxylic acid.

summary.text: Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to suspend, through December 31, 1992, the duty on (6R-(6a,7B(Z)))-7-(((2-Amino-4-thiazolyl) ((carboxymethoxy)imino)acetyl) amino)-3-ethenyl-8-0x0-5-thia-1-azabicyclo (4.2.0) oct-2-ene-2-carboxylic acid.
